{"title":"2025 Sea Otter Classic: Tailfin Equipped Cotic FlareMAX with Hope Tech – John Watson","link":"https://theradavist.com/tailfin-equipped-cotic-flaremax/","date":1744801243000,"content":"<p><em>Alongside our bigger <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/search/2025+Sea+Otter+Classic/\" target=\"_blank\">2025 Sea Otter Classic</a> showcase posts, we’re highlighting some bikes that caused pause for John and Spencer at the show. Today, we’re checking out this stunning Cotic FlareMax with Tailfin bags and Hope Tech components. Read on for John’s words and photos below…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/SeaOtter_1UP_USA_Coverage.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/SeaOtter_1UP_USA_Coverage.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/SeaOtter_1UP_USA_Coverage.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/SeaOtter_1UP_USA_Coverage.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>The Radavist thanks <a href=\"https://1up-usa.com/\" target=\"_blank\">1UP USA</a> for sponsoring our Sea Otter Classic coverage and our independent Reportage!</strong></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Cotic-Bikes-FlareMAX-Review-34a.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Cotic-Bikes-FlareMAX-Review-34a.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Cotic-Bikes-FlareMAX-Review-34a.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Cotic-Bikes-FlareMAX-Review-34a.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Johns-Cotic-Flaremax-Blue-Hour-8.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Johns-Cotic-Flaremax-Blue-Hour-8.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Johns-Cotic-Flaremax-Blue-Hour-8.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Johns-Cotic-Flaremax-Blue-Hour-8.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The Cotic FlareMax is a super fun, modified single-pivot full-suspension platform that utilizes a linkage design the brand calls “DropLink.” <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/cotic-flaremax-gen5-review/\" target=\"_blank\">My initial review</a> spurred me into getting a frame for myself last fall, which we <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/cotic-flaremax-build/\" target=\"_blank\">just debuted on The Radavist last month</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Grinduro_Scotland-02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Grinduro_Scotland-02.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Grinduro_Scotland-02.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Grinduro_Scotland-02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scotland-44.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scotland-44.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scotland-44.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Scotland-44.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>Photos from my <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/the-complete-grinduro-scotland-experience-on-the-isle-of-arran/\" target=\"_blank\">Grinduro Scotland photoshoot</a> back in 2017…</em></p>\n<p>While the previous photos of the FlareMax have been shot in dry and arid places, this photo gallery appears to be shot in the middle of <em>Haar</em> on the coast of eastern Scotland – <em>Haar</em> is vernacular for coastal fog in Scotland.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-5.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-5.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Eagle-eyed readers might note the new branding on this FlareMax<span>, not only for <a href=\"https://www.cotic.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">Cotic Bikes</a> but also for Tailfin. James told me at the booth that “only design-eyed people have noticed the change, ” which</span> is perhaps an earmark of a well-done branding exercise. It allows the brand to roll out a new look without confusing customers.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-4.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-4.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-4.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-4.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-24.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-24.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-24.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-24.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Laced with Tailfin bags, including the <a href=\"https://www.tailfin.cc/aeropack-cargo/?v=0b3b97fa6688\" target=\"_blank\">AeroPack Cargo</a> and <a href=\"https://www.tailfin.cc/product/rear-systems/rack-top-bags/ap-rack-top-bag/?v=0b3b97fa6688\" target=\"_blank\">AP18 Cargo Top Bag</a>, <a href=\"https://www.tailfin.cc/bar-bag-system/?v=0b3b97fa6688\" target=\"_blank\">Bar Bag System</a>, and a custom frame bag, this FlareMax is ready to roll into and out of coastal fog and precipitous terrain found in many of the UK’s famous touring routes.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-26.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-26.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-26.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-26.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-12.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-12.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-12.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-12.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-9.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-9.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.hopetech.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Hope Tech</a>‘s silver components complement the black bags and brightly colored ombré finish, offered by <a href=\"https://www.cotic.co.uk/news/2025/full_suspension_a_la_carte\" target=\"_blank\">Cotic’s à la Carte paint options</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-29.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-29.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-29.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Cotic-FlareMax-Tailfin-Hope-29.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>I appreciate it when brands work with local companies, and this Cotic FlareMax has a lot of UK love on it! Well done to all…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/SeaOtter_1UP_USA_Coverage.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/SeaOtter_1UP_USA_Coverage.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/SeaOtter_1UP_USA_Coverage.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/SeaOtter_1UP_USA_Coverage.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>The Radavist thanks <a href=\"https://1up-usa.com/\" target=\"_blank\">1UP USA</a> for sponsoring our Sea Otter Classic coverage and our independent Reportage!</strong></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tailfin-equipped-cotic-flaremax/\">2025 Sea Otter Classic: Tailfin Equipped Cotic FlareMAX with Hope Tech</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"4fc84af9cc58df943bad351977be359aae3d708d40c44d0e37e17101f20acec0","category":"Cycling"}